<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <div class="row">


        <div class="col">
           <img src="~/img/pngwing9.png" alt="unknown" class="img-fluid" style="width: 300px;"/>
        </div>

        <div class="col">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>At Diamond Book Shop, we’re passionate about connecting readers with the books they love through a seamless and inspiring online experience.</p>
            @* <button class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</button> *@
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#exampleModal">
                Learn More
            </button>

            <!-- Modal -->
            <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
                    <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="exampleModalLabel">Modal title</h1>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        Welcome to Diamond Book Shop, your trusted online destination for books of all kinds. Whether you're a lifelong reader, a curious learner, or someone searching for the perfect gift, we offer a carefully curated selection of titles across genres—from bestsellers and classics to indie gems and academic resources. Our mission is to make reading accessible and enjoyable for everyone, with fast shipping, secure checkout, and friendly customer service. At Diamond Book Shop, every book tells a story—and so do we.
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Save changes</button>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="col">
            <h1>Contact Us</h1>
            <p>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseWidthExample" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseWidthExample">
                    Toggle width collapse
                </button>
            </p>
            <div style="min-height: 120px;">
                <div class="collapse collapse-horizontal" id="collapseWidthExample">
                    <div class="card card-body" style="width: 300px;">
                        We’re here to help! If you have any questions, feedback, or need assistance with your order, please don’t hesitate to reach out. You can contact us via email at <a href="#">Diamond@Bookshop.com</a> or use our contact number <strong>0123456789</strong>  , and we’ll get back to you as soon as possible. Your satisfaction is important to us, and we’re always happy to hear from fellow book lovers.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-2 mt-2">
           <img src="~/img/pngwing7.png" alt="unknown" class="img-fluid" />
        </div>
       
    </div>

